    "title": "Connect Content Semantic Search",
    "description": "A hybrid semantic search engine for Posit Connect content. Combines vector embeddings (MiniLM) and full-text search (SQLite FTS5) with Reciprocal Rank Fusion to find relevant content by meaning, not just keywords. Includes a Vue 3 single-page app frontend and a background indexer that syncs content from Connect on a configurable interval.",
